---
---

<section id="lithium-comparison" class="py-20 bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-4">Why Upgrade to Lithium-Ion?</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-green-500 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">While lead-acid batteries have been the standard for decades, modern Lithium-Ion technology offers unparalleled performance, convenience, and long-term value.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl -mr-10 -mt-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-700 group-hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3x Faster Charging</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Lithium-ion batteries accept charge much faster than traditional lead-acid batteries, ensuring you are ready for the next power outage much sooner.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl -mr-10 -mt-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-700 group-hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Longer Lifespan</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Enjoy up to 4 times the cycle life of a standard lead-acid battery. A single lithium-ion battery can easily outlast multiple replacements of traditional batteries.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl -mr-10 -mt-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-700 group-hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Zero Maintenance</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Say goodbye to regular water top-ups and acid spills. Lithium-ion batteries are completely sealed and require absolutely zero active maintenance.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl -mr-10 -mt-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-700 group-hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5l-5-5m5 5v-4m0 4h-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Compact & Lightweight</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Lithium batteries pack significantly more power into a much smaller and lighter package, freeing up valuable floor space in your home or office.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl -mr-10 -mt-10 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150"></div>
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-700 group-hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">100% Usable Capacity</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Unlike lead-acid which shouldn't be discharged below 50%, lithium-ion batteries allow you to safely use up to 100% of their rated capacity.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Feature 6 (Summary/CTA) -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/40 to-slate-900 border border-green-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Upgrade?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Contact us to find the perfect Lithium-Ion setup for your calculated power requirements.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-slate-950 font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors">
          Consult an Expert
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
